PrecisEnactment of the YUKON ARCHAEOLOGICAL SITES REGULATIONS which set out detailed instructions with respect to the excavation and restoration of archaeological sites, the terms and conditions of permits, the filing of reports on work undertaken and the deposit of specimens recovered, and will come into force on June 15, 2001.
